channel.title: Server error?
channel.description: Alright, so I recently downloaded Dannyscape v4 (Delta), and I know what your first words are going to be, "Delta sucks, get a PI server you dumb faggy noob.", well you know what? I like deltas, they are easier to code, there is a larger selection of customs to choose from, etc. Anyways, I recently downloaded this source again (mainly because its the first source i ever used), and when ever I try to run the client, it doesnt work. I dont get an error or anything, it just opens a cmd window and then closes. I was wondering if this was an error with the server/source. If not, can anyone help me with this?
